msgid "gihibhāvaṃ patthayamāno … pe …"
msgstr "longing to be a householder …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.4"
msgid "asakya­put­ti­ya­bhāvaṃ patthayamāno—"
msgstr "longing not to be a son of the Sakyan,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.5"
msgid "“mātā me atthi, sā maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘I have a mother; she’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.6"
msgid "“pitā me atthi, so maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a father; he’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.7"
msgid "“bhātā me atthi, so maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a brother; he’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.8"
msgid "“bhaginī me atthi, sā maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a sister; she’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.9"
msgid "“putto me atthi, so maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a son; he’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.10"
msgid "“dhītā me atthi, sā maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a daughter; she’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.11"
msgid "“pajāpati me atthi, sā maṃ posessatī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a wife; she’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.12"
msgid "“ñātakā me atthi, te maṃ posessantī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have relations; they’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.13"
msgid "“mittā me atthi, te maṃ posessantī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have friends; they’ll support me.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.14"
msgid "“gāmo me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a village; I’ll live by means of it.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.15"
msgid "“nigamo me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have a town; I’ll live by means of it.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.16"
msgid "“khettaṃ me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have fields; I’ll live by means of them.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.17"
msgid "“vatthu me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have land; I’ll live by means of it.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.18"
msgid "“hiraññaṃ me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have gold coins; I’ll live by means of it.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.19"
msgid "“suvaṇṇaṃ me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I have gold; I’ll live by means of it.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.20"
msgid "“sippaṃ me atthi, tenāhaṃ jīvissāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘I have a profession; I’ll live by means of it.’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:63.21"
msgid "Evampi, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca apaccakkhātā."
msgstr "In this way too, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness without the training being renounced."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="57"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="MS.97" href="#MS.97">MS.97</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.1"
msgid "Atha vā pana ukkaṇṭhito anabhirato sāmaññā cavitukāmo"
msgstr "Or again, dissatisfied, discontent, desiring to give up the life of an ascetic;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.2"
msgid "bhikkhubhāvaṃ aṭṭīyamāno harāyamāno jigucchamāno"
msgstr "troubled, ashamed, and disgusted with monkhood;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.3"
msgid "Agihibhāvaṃ patthayamāno … pe …"
msgstr "longing to be a householder …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.4"
msgid "asakya­put­ti­ya­bhāvaṃ patthayamāno"
msgstr "longing not to be a son of the Sakyan,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.5"
msgid "“dukkaran”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘This is difficult to do.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.6"
msgid "“na sukaran”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘This isn’t easy to do.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.7"
msgid "“duccaran”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘This is difficult.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.8"
msgid "“na sucaran”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘This isn’t easy.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.9"
msgid "“na ussahāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I cannot endure.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.10"
msgid "“na visahāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I’m unable.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.11"
msgid "“na ramāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I don’t enjoy myself.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.12"
msgid "“nābhiramāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "‘I take no delight.’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:64.13"
msgid "Evampi kho, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca apaccakkhātā."
msgstr "In this way too, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness without the training being renounced."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="58"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.1.8.3" href="#Bu-Pj.1.8.3">Bu-Pj.1.8.3</a><a class="ms-pa" id="MS.98" href="#MS.98">MS.98</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca paccakkhātā?"
msgstr "And how is there a revealing of weakness together with the training being renounced?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhito anabhirato sāmaññā cavitukāmo"
msgstr "Here a monk is dissatisfied, discontent, desiring to give up the life of an ascetic;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.3"
msgid "bhikkhubhāvaṃ aṭṭīyamāno harāyamāno jigucchamāno"
msgstr "troubled, ashamed, and disgusted with monkhood;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.4"
msgid "gihibhāvaṃ patthayamāno … pe …"
msgstr "longing to be a householder …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.5"
msgid "asakya­put­ti­ya­bhāvaṃ patthayamāno—"
msgstr "longing not to be a son of the Sakyan, and he says and declares:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.6"
msgid "“buddhaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "‘I renounce the Buddha.’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:65.7"
msgid "Evampi, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca paccakkhātā."
msgstr "In this way, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness together with the training being renounced."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="59"></a><a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.27"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="MS.99" href="#MS.99">MS.99</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.1"
msgid "Atha vā pana ukkaṇṭhito anabhirato sāmaññā cavitukāmo"
msgstr "Or again, dissatisfied, discontent, desiring to give up the life of an ascetic;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.2"
msgid "bhikkhubhāvaṃ aṭṭīyamāno harāyamāno jigucchamāno"
msgstr "troubled, ashamed, and disgusted with monkhood;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.3"
msgid "gihibhāvaṃ patthayamāno … pe …"
msgstr "longing to be a householder …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.4"
msgid "asakya­put­ti­ya­bhāvaṃ patthayamāno—"
msgstr "longing not to be a son of the Sakyan,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.5"
msgid "“dhammaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘I renounce the Teaching’ …"

#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.27" href="#Vin.3.27">Vin 3.27</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.6"
msgid "“saṃghaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce the Order’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.7"
msgid "“sikkhaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce the practice’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.8"
msgid "“vinayaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce the training’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.9"
msgid "“pātimokkhaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce the monastic code’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.10"
msgid "“uddesaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce the recital’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.11"
msgid "“upajjhāyaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce my preceptor’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.12"
msgid "“ācariyaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce my teacher’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.13"
msgid "“sad­dhi­vihā­ri­kaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce being a student’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.14"
msgid "“antevāsikaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce being a pupil’ …"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.1.46" href="#BD.1.46">BD.1.46</a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.15"
msgid "“samā­nu­paj­jhā­ya­kaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce our common preceptor’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.16"
msgid "“samā­nā­cari­ya­kaṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘I renounce our common teacher’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.17"
msgid "“sabrahmacāriṃ paccakkhāmī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘I renounce my fellow monks’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.18"
msgid "“gihīti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘Consider me a householder’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.19"
msgid "“upāsakoti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘Consider me a lay-follower’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.20"
msgid "“ārāmikoti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘Consider me a monastery attendant’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.21"
msgid "“sāmaṇeroti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘Consider me a novice monk’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.22"
msgid "“titthiyoti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘Consider me an adherent of another sect’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.23"
msgid "“­titthi­ya­sā­vakoti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘Consider me a follower of another sect’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.24"
msgid "“assamaṇoti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘Consider me not an ascetic’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.25"
msgid "“asakya­putti­yoti maṃ dhārehī”ti vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "‘Consider me not a son of the Sakyan.’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:66.26"
msgid "Evampi, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca paccakkhātā."
msgstr "In this way too, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness together with the training being renounced."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="60"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="MS.100" href="#MS.100">MS.100</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.1"
msgid "Atha vā pana ukkaṇṭhito anabhirato sāmaññā cavitukāmo"
msgstr "Or again, dissatisfied, discontent, desiring to give up the life of an ascetic;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.2"
msgid "bhikkhubhāvaṃ aṭṭīyamāno harāyamāno jigucchamāno"
msgstr "troubled, ashamed, and disgusted with monkhood;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.3"
msgid "gihibhāvaṃ patthayamāno … pe …"
msgstr "longing to be a householder …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.4"
msgid "asakya­put­ti­ya­bhāvaṃ patthayamāno—"
msgstr "longing not to be a son of the Sakyan,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.5"
msgid "“alaṃ me buddhenā”ti vadati viññāpeti … pe …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘I’m done with the Buddha’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.6"
msgid "“alaṃ me sabrahmacārīhī”ti vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "‘I’m done with my fellow monks.’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.7"
msgid "Evampi … pe …"
msgstr "In this way too, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness together with the training being renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.8"
msgid "atha vā pana … pe …"
msgstr "Or again …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.9"
msgid "“kiṃ nu me buddhenā”ti vadati viññāpeti … pe …"
msgstr "he says and declares: ‘No more of the Buddha for me’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.10"
msgid "“kiṃ nu me sabrahmacārīhī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘No more of my fellow monks for me.’ In this way too, monks …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.11"
msgid "“na mamattho buddhenā”ti vadati viññāpeti … pe …"
msgstr "Or again … he says and declares: ‘The Buddha is of no use to me’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.12"
msgid "“na mamattho sabrahmacārīhī”ti vadati viññāpeti …"
msgstr "‘My fellow monks are of no use to me.’ In this way too, monks …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.13"
msgid "“sumuttāhaṃ buddhenā”ti vadati viññāpeti … pe …"
msgstr "Or again … he says and declares: ‘I’m well freed from the Buddha.’ …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.14"
msgid "“sumuttāhaṃ sabrahmacārīhī”ti vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "‘I’m well freed from my fellow monks.’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:67.15"
msgid "Evampi, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca paccakkhātā."
msgstr "In this way too, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness together with the training being renounced."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="61"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="MS.101" href="#MS.101">MS.101</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:68.1"
msgid "Yāni vā panaññānipi atthi buddha­ve­vaca­nāni vā dhamma­ve­vaca­nāni vā saṃgha­ve­vaca­nāni vā sikkhā­ve­vaca­nāni vā vinaya­ve­vaca­nāni vā pāti­mokkha­ve­vaca­nāni vā uddesa­ve­vaca­nāni vā upaj­jhā­ya­ve­vaca­nāni vā ācari­ya­ve­vaca­nāni vā sad­dhi­vihā­ri­ka­ve­vaca­nāni vā antevā­si­ka­ve­vaca­nāni vā samā­nu­paj­jhā­ya­ka­ve­vaca­nāni vā samā­nā­cari­ya­ka­ve­vaca­nāni vā sab­rahma­cāri­ve­vaca­nāni vā gihivevacanāni vā upāsa­ka­ve­vaca­nāni vā ārāmi­ka­ve­vaca­nāni vā sāma­ṇera­ve­vaca­nāni vā ­titthi­ya­ve­vaca­nāni vā ­titthi­ya­sāvaka­ve­vaca­nāni vā assama­ṇa­ve­vaca­nāni vā asakya­put­ti­ya­ve­vaca­nāni vā,"
msgstr "Or whatever other synonyms there are for the Buddha, for the Teaching, for the Order of monks, for the practice, for the training, for the monastic code, for the recital, for a preceptor, for a teacher, for a student, for a pupil, for a common preceptor, for a common teacher, for a fellow monk, for a householder, for a lay-follower, for a monastery attendant, for a novice monk, for an adherent of another sect, for a follower of another sect, for not being an ascetic, or for not being a son of the Sakyan—"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:68.2"
msgid "tehi ākārehi tehi liṅgehi tehi nimittehi vadati viññāpeti."
msgstr "he speaks and declares by way of these indications, by way of these marks, by way of these signs."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:68.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dubbal­yā­vi­kammañ­ceva hoti sikkhā ca paccakkhātā."
msgstr "In this way, monks, thereʼs a revealing of weakness together with the training being renounced."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="62"></a><a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.28"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.1.8.4" href="#Bu-Pj.1.8.4">Bu-Pj.1.8.4</a><a class="ms-pa" id="MS.102" href="#MS.102">MS.102</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā?"
msgstr "And how is the training not renounced?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, yehi ākārehi yehi liṅgehi yehi nimittehi sikkhā paccakkhātā hoti tehi ākārehi tehi liṅgehi tehi nimittehi ummattako sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one renounces the training by way of these indications, by way of these marks, by way of these signs, but oneʼs insane, then the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.3"
msgid "Ummattakassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one renounces the training in the presence of one whoʼs insane, the training isnʼt renounced."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.1.47" href="#BD.1.47">BD.1.47</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.4"
msgid "Khittacitto sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one whoʼs deranged renounces the training, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.5"
msgid "Khittacittassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one renounces the training in the presence of one whoʼs deranged, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.6"
msgid "Vedanāṭṭo sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one whoʼs overwhelmed by pain renounces the training, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.7"
msgid "Vedanāṭṭassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one renounces the training in the presence of one whoʼs overwhelmed by pain, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.8"
msgid "Devatāya santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one renounces the training to a god, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.9"
msgid "Tiracchā­na­gatassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If one renounces the training to an animal, the training isnʼt renounced."

#. <span class=\\\"var\\\" title=\\\"milakkhakassa (s1-3) | milakkhukassa (pts1) | milakkhussa (mr)\\\" id=\\\"note43\\\">milakkhassa</span>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.10"
msgid "Ariyakena milakkhassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, so ca na paṭivijānāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If an Indian renounces the training to a foreigner who doesnʼt understand him, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.11"
msgid "Milakkhakena ariyassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, so ca na paṭivijānāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If a foreigner renounces the training to an Indian who doesnʼt understand him, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.12"
msgid "Ariyakena ariyassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, so ca na paṭivijānāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If an Indian renounces the training to another Indian who doesnʼt understand him, the training isnʼt renounced."

#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.28" href="#Vin.3.28">Vin 3.28</a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.13"
msgid "Milakkhakena milakkhassa santike sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, so ca na paṭivijānāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If a foreigner renounces the training to another foreigner who doesnʼt understand him, the training isnʼt renounced."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj1:69.14"
msgid "Davāya sikkhaṃ paccakkhāti, apaccakkhātā hoti sikkhā."
msgstr "If he renounces the training as a joke, the training isnʼt renounced."

